C ++********************************************************************
C                                                                      *
C FLUSHRESULTS.F    NEW                         NOV 2000 ARDEAN LEITH
C                   CHANGED VERBOSE             JUN 2004 ARDEAN LEITH                                                           *
C                   defined (SP_GFORTRAN)       DEC 2005 ARDEAN LEITH
